powerpc: Remove BITOP_MASK and BITOP_WORD from asm/bitops.h

Replace BITOP_MASK and BITOP_WORD with BIT_MASK and BIT_WORD defined
in linux/bitops.h and remove BITOP_* which are not used anymore.

